@{PARD}
@{B}Brainstormer Description:@{UB}@{PAR}

Brainstormers are a lizard-like creature of about 7' in length. They are a dull
yellow in color with small green and red speckles. Hatchlings are light brown
with no speckles. Brainstormers have a very keen sense of smell and also have
infravision out to 60'.@{PAR}

