@{PARD}
@{B}Brainstormer Ecology:@{UB}@{PAR}

Brainstormers eat small and medium-sized rodents and snakes, but have also been
known to eat the flesh of larger creatures (such as humanoids) they have killed
for treasure. Brainstormer blood is an ingredient in the ink used to create a 
power word, stun scroll.@{PAR}

